#IntoAmerica: As the 2020 DNC has come to a close, did the Democrats do enough to connect with young Black voters?  

.@trymainelee talks to activist @JamiraBurley, who hopes the party will seize on opportunities to inspire young voters of color.

text: Brayden Harrington, the teen who shared his story on the final night of the Democratic National Convention about how Joe Biden helped him with his stutter, tells @NBCNews it has boosted his confidence and is pushing him to help other kids like him. https://t.co/auefTwA7Ka
